data.description: 4 BEDROOMS PLUS A COVERED PATIO IN SOUTH WALTON COUNTY. Single story home on the largest lot in the community backing up to a nature preserve. The master bedroom suite features a tray ceiling with in suite master bath that has double granite vanities, separate tiled shower, garden tub and water closet, plus a big walk-in closet. The home also has a nice covered patio, 2 car garage, separate laundry room with cabinets, large family room with a breakfast area off of the kitchen, stainless steel, high end appliances and an eat-in bar. Beautiful wood flooring in master bedroom, foyer, living room, kitchen and breakfast area as well as 19'' x 19'' ceramic tile in the baths and laundry room. Located close to schools, parks, dining, shopping, and beaches! Washer and dryer provided.
